</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/m3p1REJQEjY" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/10/17/animal-crossing-new-horizons-has-some-big-updates/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=animal-crossing-new-horizons-has-some-big-updates</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>日本最大電訊商網絡故障　200 萬手機用戶斷網大半天</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/5FF1heQNeRg/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[藍骨]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sun, 17 Oct 2021 14:50:56 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[DOCOMO]]></category><category><![CDATA[日本]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1066103</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>流動網絡已經是生活必須，如果系統出現大規模故障，很多人都會感到不便。最近日本 Docomo 就發生全國網絡故障，用戶斷網大半天，成為當地大新聞。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>流動網絡已經是生活必須，如果系統出現大規模故障，很多人都會感到不便。最近日本 Docomo 就發生全國網絡故障，用戶斷網大半天，成為當地大新聞。<br /><span id="more-1066103"></span></p><p>NTT Docomo 是日本最大的電訊商，因此不少日本人都會信賴其服務可靠。不過在當地時間 10 月 14 日下午 5 點開始，全國 Docomo 網絡用戶（包括使用其網絡的 MVNO 電訊商）都無法連接電話和互聯網，受影響用戶人數多達 200 萬。直到翌日凌晨 5 點左右才逐步恢復 5G/LTE 服務，3G 服務更要到晚上才恢復。</p><p>Docomo 方面之後召開記者會致歉，表示問題原因為升級 IoT 伺服器時發生問題，導致網絡出演異常擁擠，因此實施了 100% 全網流量限制，連同 3G、LTE 和 5G 網絡一併受到影響。限制逐步解除之後由於大量用家一次過湧入，導致網絡再次超載令問題持續。日本政府方面亦表示非常遺憾，要求徹查問題防止再次發生。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20211015/k10013308501000.html">NHK</a></p>
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=5FF1heQNeRg:gvS79pDBnQU:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=5FF1heQNeRg:gvS79pDBnQU:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/5FF1heQNeRg" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/10/17/ntt-docomos-mobile-network-disrupted-in-japan/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=ntt-docomos-mobile-network-disrupted-in-japan</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>【有片睇】日本佛像配航拍機，實現在天飄遊影片超神幻</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/IYkr3Vt300I/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sun, 17 Oct 2021 14:13:35 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1066111</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>佛像在好多劇集中都坐著雲團在天空上飄遊。而日本最近有寺廟製作飛天佛像，利用了航拍機實現了佛像浮遊飛行。 &#038;nb [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>佛像在好多劇集中都坐著雲團在天空上飄遊。而日本最近有寺廟製作飛天佛像，利用了航拍機實現了佛像浮遊飛行。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.05.42.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1066112" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.05.42-694x386.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.05.42-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.05.42-1280x713.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.05.42-768x428.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.05.42-1536x855.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.05.42-2048x1140.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.05.42.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.05.20.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1066113" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.05.20-694x402.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="402" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.05.20-694x402.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.05.20-1280x741.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.05.20-768x445.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.05.20-1536x889.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.05.20-2048x1186.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.05.20.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>日本京都土御門佛所的三浦耀山佛師，最新使用航拍機製作了會飛天的佛像。他表示這個飛天神佛能夠浮遊空中，演繹了日本平安時代開始神佛在天飄浮的神話。過往寺廟只能在牆壁上貼上神佛在天飄浮的繪畫，但使用了現代技術，利用航拍機就可載著佛像在天上飄浮。而在影片當中，更以乾冰營造了更有氣氛的效果。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.17.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1066114" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.17-694x387.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.17-694x387.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.17-1280x713.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.17-768x428.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.17.jpg 1360w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.28.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1066115" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.28-694x467.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="467" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.28-694x467.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.28-1280x862.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.28-768x517.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.28-1536x1034.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.28-2048x1379.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.28.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.36.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1066116" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.36-694x490.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="490" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.36-694x490.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.36-1275x900.jpg 1275w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.36-768x542.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.36-1536x1084.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.36.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.40.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1066117" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.40-694x497.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="497" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.40-694x497.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.09.40-1257x900.jpg 1257w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 10.0