 width="462" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 9.56.37-462x580.jpg 462w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 9.56.37-718x900.jpg 718w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 9.56.37-768x963.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-17-下午 9.56.37.jpg 810w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 462px" /></a></p><p>此次發佈會除了很大機會出現使用最新 M1X／M2 晶片的最新版 MacBook Pro，更有可能會出現 AirPods 第三代產品。</p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=XDFYnVd4FU8:aS_NCnMXpUA:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=XDFYnVd4FU8:aS_NCnMXpUA:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
